description:
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Administrator to provide professional administrative support to the Audiology Team. The post holder will be responsible providing a full range of administrative support to the team. The successful candidate will support the head of service to ensure that the service runs effectively and efficiently and that referrers, partners, service users and their families/carers experience a responsive and friendly service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should have significant proven experience with excellent organisational and communication skills. Key responsibilities for this role include supporting the clinical team on a day to day basis, telephone management, audits, downloading and reporting, copy typing, audio typing, monthly meeting minutes etc. You will be expected to prioritise tasks as well as use your initiative and organise your own time. It is essential you have an excellent working knowledge of the Microsoft Office package.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be required to work with minimum supervision and take initiative in prioritizing their workload to ensure service objective are met.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Rosbin Syed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title:Head of Audiology&lt;/p&gt;
